Edit the last sql statement. Compare with → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus/edit[SQL*Plus' edit] command. Apparently, the editor can be configured by setting `sqlcmdeditor`:
code {
set sqlcmdeditor=notepad
:ed
code }

